- app.init(), app.handle(), app.run_all(): these call the above functions and are unaffected.
- plugins.load_plugins(): performs register(...); register writes to the underlying _handlers dict; since MappingProxyType view reflects updates, readers still see new handlers.

I did not modify any write operations (register, clear) or replace any write functions, preserving write semantics and overwrite behavior.

